member.name: T:Apizr.Progressing.ApizrProgressStream
member.summary: This implementation of registers how much data has been read (received) versus written (sent) for a particular HTTP operation. The implementation is client side in that the total bytes to send is taken from the request and the total bytes to read is taken from the response. In a server side scenario, it would be the other way around (reading the request and writing the response).
